Class MessageToClient

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.gc19.Networking.Server.Message.MessageToClient
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AnswerToActionMessage, ConfigurationMessage, GameHandlingMessage, NetworkHandlingErrorMessage, NotifyChatMessage, NotifyEventOnGame, ServerHeartBeatMessage, TurnStateMessage
public abstract class MessageToClient extends Object implements Serializable
This abstract class represents a generic message that server can send to client. Every message has its own priority.
